reviewText: I like all the tv series from that era. The tv series from 50's is so entertaining.

I've seen most of these episodes by scrounging online and looking through the archives. I would suggest buying this to watch the final episode dubbed the Haunting which I wasn't able to find online.

It is about a poltergeist that haunts his friend for abandoning him.
If you are an OSB fan and remember what TV looked like in that era, this will be a fun trip down memory lane.
I enjoyed seeing Joan Fontaine in this dvd, but, being an early tv show, it lacked the quality of her movies.
